data.title: Jonas Roeser on LinkedIn: CBD Move Free Officially Announces Board of Directors and New Product…
data.text:
I first met Kjell Schei as a teenager during an evening SAT prep course. Despite attending different high schools, we quickly became friends. Over the years, our friendship has grown, and we've collaborated on various projects. I'm honored to have been entrusted with the branding and public relations for his new venture, Agere Automotive. Enjoy their first “Media Get” below!

I am thrilled to share GREY Journal just launched a new Feature article in their Inspire page that highlights my previous interview. Grey Journal is an amazing resource for entrepreneurs check out the article at the link below

I am privileged to have crafted the company's logo and branding, as well as to serve on the Advisory Board for GyftHint.

Dear colleagues in the insurance industry, I am excited to announce the relaunch of Agent Review with an enhanced platform boasting over a dozen AI features to bolster your digital advertising and online visibility. Click below and simply provide your email to discover more about our 2.0 launch.
